                     <interp inst="t17820911-36-off180" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing seven pounds weight of hard soap, value 3 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17820911-36-victim416" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Whitchurch
                  <interp inst="t17820911-36-victim416" type="surname" value="Whitchurch"></interp>
